6:
More and more people are coming
to see us every day! We're gonna
conquer the country in no time at
this rate!
14:
What's up with you? Come on, you
gotta get pumped if you wanna put
on a good show!
18: Oh, there you guys are! Yo!
24:
You guys ready to go? We can help
if you need anything done.
29:
You're supposed to kick back and
enjoy the show! Y'know, as thanks
for helping us out with the whole
throwdown.
33:
Speaking of which... You're looking
pretty good for someone who went
toe to toe with a monster.
37: Unlike a certain somebody else here.
42:
I know, I know, I'm a zombie. 
I shouldn't get tired...
44:
But my soul just about left my body
after all that craziness...
49:
Worrying's not gonna do you any
good! You gotta be ready to handle
whatever life throws at you!
54: Yeow, ow, ow! I can't help it, okay!
59:
What's there to worry about
anyways? She's got more guts than
Alk, and he's the one who spends his
days adventuring.
63:
Hell yeah I do! Thanks for the
shout-out, man!
67:
...Those two get along really well,
don't they.
71:
Like two peas in a pod. A really wild
pod...
77:
Woo, thanks for coming! We'll be
back after a quick break!
82:
Your concerts are pretty easygoing
compared to other ones, I gotta say.
84:
Almost makes me nervous that
people are gonna swarm you or
cause a riot though...
88:
Ehhh, we're already used to people
crashing the show.
90:
Besides, these folks'll listen to what 
I say if I put my foot down.
94:
I guess some people are into the
idea of an idol that can kick their
butt.
98:
Could really light a fire under folks
with an attitude like that. Even teach
'em how to fight.
102:
See, he gets it! That's how I'm gonna
take over the country as an idol!
103:
We should throw hands one of these
days when I'm free!
107:
Saki-chan, how many times do I
have to tell you...
111:
I'll still be mainly doing idol stuff, so
you've got nothing to worry about!
113:
Anyways, that's probably a long
enough break—
123:
I got something I wanna say before
we keep going. Come here.
134:
...You're free to have your little
performances now, so why are you
dragging me into this?
140: Yo, do you guys know who this is?
142: Of course! We all know Symphonia!
144:
So the other day, me and her had 
a serious showdown...
146:
We were neck and neck the whole
time—and every minute of it was
awesome. Felt like my soul was on
fire.
149:
Easy for you to say. You were the
one who won...
152:
So that's why... We're gonna have a
showdown concert in front of you
guys! That way you can all get fired
up too!
155:
Whoa... A concert with
Franchouchou AND Symphonia?
That'd be sick!
156:
Ain't nothing more spicy than a
battle between rivals!
159:
We'll announce the details later, 
so keep a lookout!
165:
Loser has to do what the winner
says, remember?
168:
They got along so poorly in the
beginning, but now look at them.
171:
You better bring out all the stops for
this concert.
172:
Not that it matters—I'll still be better,
and everyone will see that I am.
178:
We need to get permission to hold
another show though...
182:
Eh, we'll work something out! Sweat
the small things later!
186:
Hey, don't be a stranger either. Show
or no show, I'm down to go anytime
you wanna.
188:
I won't run away or hide. I'll always
face things head on—full throttle!
